              li.mb-2: a(href="#comparison") Social Drinking vs. Problem Drinking
              li.mb-2: a(href="#process") The Step-by-Step Path to Recovery
              li.mb-2: a(href="#mistakes") Common Pitfalls to Avoid
              li.mb-2: a(href="#faq") Frequently Asked Questions
